that she promised to return the money

00:26:34.782 --> 00:26:36.534
and not to expose them.

00:26:36.617 --> 00:26:40.579
But he said you can't undo
what's been done,

00:26:40.663 --> 00:26:44.458
and that if word gets out,
he'd come after her.

00:26:44.542 --> 00:26:47.586
I haven't been able
to reach her since then.

00:26:48.587 --> 00:26:49.422
Ms. Wi.

00:26:51.173 --> 00:26:53.884
That man is seriously dangerous, isn't he?

00:26:56.679 --> 00:26:57.888
If you want this to end,

00:26:58.722 --> 00:27:01.434
you have to tell me the truth
about everything.

00:27:02.184 --> 00:27:05.312
Everything about that man,
and about Gwon Se-na as well.

00:27:13.696 --> 00:27:18.367
When you were at the Geumsang Arts Awards…

00:27:19.160 --> 00:27:20.244
That night,

00:27:20.870 --> 00:27:23.247
the chairman you asked questions to…

00:27:24.748 --> 00:27:26.000
It was him.

00:27:27.585 --> 00:27:29.879
